---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Dead Beta
---
<div class="home">
  <div class="home-intro">
    <span class="label">v0.∞ — always in beta</span>
    <h1>Analysis, experiments,<br>and open failures.</h1>
    <p>Essays on data, energy, finance, culture, and whatever else demands an explanation. Written with a humble awareness that I might be wrong.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="post-list">
    {% for post in collections.posts %}
      <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-list-item">
        <div class="item-date">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</div>
        <div class="item-body">
          {% if post.data.tags %}
            <div class="item-tags">
              {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
                {% if tag != "posts" %}
                  <span class="tag">{{ tag }}</span>
                {% endif %}
              {% endfor %}
            </div>
          {% endif %}
          <div class="item-title">{{ post.data.title }}</div>
          {% if post.data.description %}
            <div class="item-deck">{{ post.data.description }}</div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>
